summary: Whatever you do, don't think about Peter being upset because he had the Gauntlet and he could've stopped Tony from getting to...
body:
Whatever you do, don’t think about Peter being upset because he had the Gauntlet and he could’ve stopped Tony from getting to it.

And whatever you do, don’t imagine Peter Parker crying, wishing he had worn the Gauntlet and snapped so Tony could live.
